something serious this time.

02:05.625 --> 02:07.794
It's a rash.

02:07.877 --> 02:09.545
She's in denial.

02:09.628 --> 02:10.713
Poor thing.

02:10.797 --> 02:12.590
{\an1}Now, let me say
good-bye to my bird.

02:12.674 --> 02:14.884
Good-bye, Turdy.

02:14.968 --> 02:18.555
{\an1}Papa's got to go away
for a while.

02:18.638 --> 02:20.515
{\an1}Remember who loves you
the most.

02:20.598 --> 02:22.392
(<i> shrieks</i> )

02:22.475 --> 02:23.059
That's right.

02:23.143 --> 02:25.687
{\an1}Papa loves you
the most.

02:25.770 --> 02:28.356
{\an1}Kiss him
good-bye, Hutch.

02:28.439 --> 02:30.608
I don't want to kiss
the bird, Filburt.

02:30.692 --> 02:33.027
Kiss the bird!

02:33.111 --> 02:34.404
(<i> crows cawing</i> )

02:34.487 --> 02:36.406
Good luck, Rocko.

02:36.489 --> 02:37.991
Bye, Dr. Hutchinson.

02:38.074 --> 02:39.033
Good-bye, Filburt.

02:39.117 --> 02:40.702
(<i> shrieks</i> )

02:41.661 --> 02:42.537
Hmm.

02:42.620 --> 02:43.746
Let's see.

02:43.830 --> 02:46.749
{\an1}"Keep caged and
minimize excitement."

02:54.340 --> 02:55.258
He's boring.

02:55.341 --> 02:57.218
{\an1}No, he's
a lovely bird.

02:59.596 --> 03:01.514
Just look at
what a lovely bird he...

