(<i> screaming</i> )

03:04.142 --> 03:04.893
Help me!
Help me!

03:04.976 --> 03:08.104
(<i> screaming</i> )

03:08.187 --> 03:10.148
Hang on, Rocko!

03:17.655 --> 03:19.365
Stupid bird.

03:19.449 --> 03:21.367
(<i> Turdy shrieks</i> )

03:21.451 --> 03:22.285
He's out!

03:22.368 --> 03:23.494
(<i> barking and crashing</i> )

03:23.578 --> 03:24.454
Get him, Spunky.

03:24.537 --> 03:25.455
Get the bird!

03:25.538 --> 03:26.998
No, Spunky, no!

03:27.081 --> 03:27.957
Whoo!

03:28.041 --> 03:30.126
Leave the bird alone!

03:31.461 --> 03:32.962
Spunky!

03:33.046 --> 03:35.548
{\an1}Bad, bird!
Bad!

03:35.632 --> 03:37.884
{\an1}Spunky, are you
all right?

03:37.967 --> 03:38.885
Nasty old bird.

03:38.968 --> 03:40.803
(<i> shrieks</i> )

03:43.056 --> 03:45.600
(<i> crashing on TV</i> )

03:49.562 --> 03:50.146
Hey, Rock?

03:50.229 --> 03:52.357
{\an1}You want to move
to France?

03:52.440 --> 03:54.317
Not really, no.

03:54.400 --> 03:56.110
Yeah, me neither.

03:56.194 --> 03:57.070
(<i> Rocko screams</i> )

03:57.153 --> 03:58.404
The bird's out!

04:02.325 --> 04:02.825
Turdy!

