HEFFER:
Hold on!

12:37.756 --> 12:40.217
I'm headed straight
for a crowded health spa!

12:40.301 --> 12:41.302
Get out of the way!

12:41.385 --> 12:42.386
{\an1}My brakes
are failing.

12:42.470 --> 12:47.391
{\an5}HEFFER:
I'm popping
a wheelie!

12:47.475 --> 12:50.561
{\an1}Great race last week
at Teddy's house.

12:50.644 --> 12:53.772
{\an1}Too bad your car exploded
in the third turn.

12:53.856 --> 12:54.940
{\an3}Yeah.

12:55.024 --> 12:57.776
{\an5}Where do you think
Teddy's family
is living now?

12:57.860 --> 12:59.403
Aren't you guys
a little too old

12:59.487 --> 13:01.113
to still be
in the Weasel Scouts?

13:01.197 --> 13:03.657
{\an1}It's a way
of life, Rocko.

13:03.741 --> 13:06.035
Yeah, but for 12 years?

13:06.118 --> 13:08.204
That's enough
questions, philistine!

13:08.287 --> 13:10.664
Just get us
to the meeting on time.

13:12.500 --> 13:13.459
(<i> gasps</i> )

13:13.542 --> 13:14.543
Stop the car!

13:14.627 --> 13:15.544
(<i> tires screech</i> )

13:15.628 --> 13:17.922
Oh, thank goodness,
it's the W...

13:18.005 --> 13:20.049
(<i> smack; woman groans</i> )

13:20.132 --> 13:21.592
Two, please.

13:21.675 --> 13:24.678
HEFFER:
Thank you.

13:24.762 --> 13:27.223
(<i> smack; woman groans</i> )

13:28.390 --> 13:29.558
(<i> chanting</i> ):
One, one, one-two-three

13:29.642 --> 13:31.560
Let's all climb the weasel tree

13:31.644 --> 13:33.771
Three, three, three-four-five

13:33.854 --> 13:36.065
Let's all do the weasel jive.

13:36.148 --> 13:38.859
WEASEL TROOP:
Five, five, five-six-seven

13:38.943 --> 13:40.528
Let's all go to weasel heaven

13:40.611 --> 13:41.529
Seven, seven, eight-nine-ten

13:41.612 --> 13:44.990
Let's all do it over again.

13:45.074 --> 13:46.909
La, la, la-la-la

13:46.992 --> 13:48.994
La-la la-la la-la-la.

13:51.830 --> 13:53.290
Here they come.

13:54.500 --> 13:57.127
There, there--
it's okay, Teddy.

